##Evidence Position

def classify_evidence_position(gold_idx, n_docs):
    pct = (gold_idx + 1) / n_docs
    if pct <= 0.33:
        return "beginning"
    elif pct <= 0.66:
        return "middle"
    else:
        return "end"



gold_idx → position of gold doc (starts from 0)
n_docs → total docs in ctxs


Example: 
pos = classify_evidence_position(0, 4)  # → "beginning"
pos = classify_evidence_position(2, 4)  # → "end"

